| `authClient.organization.removeMember` | `POST /organization/remove-member` | Remove member | Body: `{ memberIdOrEmail, organizationId? }` |
| `authClient.organization.updateMemberRole` | `POST /organization/update-member-role` | Change member role | Body: `{ memberId, role, organizationId? }` |
| `authClient.organization.leave` | `POST /organization/leave` | Leave org | Body: `{ organizationId }` |

#### Reactive Stores (nanostores atoms)

The client plugin exposes reactive stores via nanostores:

```typescript
