### Risks and Mitigations

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Existing sessions lack `activeOrganizationId` | Analytics return empty for logged-in users | Fallback to `user.id` in `orgMiddleware`; migration script updates existing sessions |
| Slug uniqueness collisions during migration | Migration script fails | Generate slugs with uniqueness suffix; catch and retry |
| better-auth `organization()` plugin adds routes that conflict | Auth endpoint clashes | The plugin uses `/api/auth/organization/*` prefix which doesn't conflict with existing routes |
| TanStack Query cache stale after org switch | User sees wrong org's data | Invalidate all queries on org switch |
| CLI users without `.rudel.json` after update | Sessions go to wrong org | Fallback chain: `.rudel.json` > `session.activeOrganizationId` > `user.id` |
| Old CLI versions in the wild | Missing `organizationId` in ingest | Field is optional; server falls back to session's active org or `user.id` |

